    • getTemplatesMap

      public static Map<String,String> getTemplatesMap()
      Retrieves a copy of the current API response templates map.

      This method returns a new HashMap containing the entries from the TEMPLATES_DATA map. The returned map is a shallow copy, meaning modifications to the returned map will not affect the original TEMPLATES_DATA map.

      Returns:
      A new Map containing the API response templates. The map's keys are template identifiers, and the values are the corresponding response template strings.
